Package com.i2group.disco.audit

Class NoOpAuditLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.disco.audit.NoOpAuditLogger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAuditLogger
    public final class NoOpAuditLogger
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAuditLogger
    A trivial implementation of IAuditLogger that performs no logging. When audit logging is not required, this is an efficient option.
    Since:
    8.0
